    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Google Maps Reviews Crawler (SerpAPI -> Google Sheets)\n\n### Purpose\nCollect Google Maps reviews for selected car wash locations and save normalized review rows to Google Sheets.\n\n### Flow\n1. Trigger manually or by schedule\n2. Read location rows from sheet TPHCM\n3. Filter rows (currently: rating = 5 AND district = quan 1)\n4. Loop each location and call SerpAPI google_maps_reviews by place_id\n5. Parse Reviews flattens nested JSON into one row per review\n6. Append or update into sheet TPHCM_Reviews using review_id as key\n\n### Output fields\n- place: place_id, place_name, place_address, place_rating, place_type\n- reviewer: reviewer_name, reviewer_id, local_guide, review_count, photo_count\n- review: rating, review_text, translated_text, date, likes, images_json, link\n- crawl metadata: crawl_date, crawl_timestamp\n\n### Notes\n- Dedup/upsert key: review_id\n- If no translated text exists, review_text_translated is empty\n- Parse node supports multiple incoming items and array payloads",
        "height": 560,
        "width": 820
      },
      "id": "c86545e0-b6a3-4d59-a5f2-7f3417bd38ad",
